                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9278" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">SCLM-0230</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1479 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小米逆袭记：从供应链危机到韧性崛起之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Xiaomi＇s Resurgence: From Supply Chain Crisis to Resilient Growth</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">叶英平，杨中洲，肖桂玉</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">吉林大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小米科技有限责任公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">通讯业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">供应链韧性；供应链战略；供应链管理；供应链重构；</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"> Supply Chain Resilience;Supply Chain Strategy; Supply Chain Management; Supply Chain Restructuring</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在全球化逆流加剧的背景下，供应链可能随时面临中断风险，众多企业的供应链管理正经历严峻挑战。不确定性和复杂性成为企业运营中不可忽视的关键问题。本案例聚焦于小米公司在供应链管理中遇到的一系列挑战，及其应对策略，描述了小米在供应链上游面临断货风险、中游遇到生产瓶颈、下游面临销售与服务问题时的应对措施，回顾了小米如何提升供应链韧性，克服挑战，实现持续发展。本案例旨在引导学生理解供应链韧性的概念与重要性，掌握拉动式和推动式供应链战略的相关知识，熟悉供应链全生命周期管理概念及各阶段内容，培养创新思维与解决问题能力，进而能将所学应用于实际，提高解决实际问题能力。此外，本案例也可为企业提高供应链韧性提供一定的借鉴参考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In the context of intensifying globalization reversals, supply chains may face disruption risks at any time, posing severe challenges to the supply chain management of numerous enterprises. Uncertainty and complexity have become critical issues that cannot be ignored in business operations. This case study focuses on the series of challenges faced by Xiaomi in supply chain management and its response strategies. It details Xiaomi&#39;s measures to address risks at the upstream stage such as stock outages, production bottlenecks in the midstream, and sales and service issues at the downstream stage. The study also reviews how Xiaomi enhanced its supply chain resilience, overcame challenges, and achieved sustainable development. The aim of this case is to guide students in understanding the concept and importance of supply chain resilience, mastering the knowledge related to pull and push supply chain strategies, familiarizing with the entire lifecycle management concepts of the supply chain, cultivating innovative thinking and problem-solving skills, and ultimately applying these skills to practical situations to enhance their ability to solve real-world problems. Additionally, this case study can also provide useful references for companies seeking to improve their supply chain resilience.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《供应链管理》、《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">供应链韧性；供应链战略；供应链协同管理；战略实施和运营管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-02</td>
                            </tr>
